    <h2> Keeping a bestfriend guide </h2>
    <p> Having a bestfriend is fun, but can be hard to keep.<br> 
      This guide will help you keep your bestfriend, and make more.<br>
      So here are some steps to help: </p> 
    <li> Be honest- </li> 
    <p>:being hones with a bestfriend is a key part in staying loyal and not lying to lose there trust.</p>
    <li> Help out- </li>
    <p> :helping someone who is supposed to be your bestfriend is such a big idea, helping them when there sad, or when you've upset them, especially if there just having a rough time.</p> 
    <li> Having fun- </li> 
    <p> Having fun with your bestfriend is a must! </p> 
